k reported: The\u00a0Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Allah Almighty said: O son of Adam, if you call upon Me and place your hope in Me, I will forgive you despite what is within you and I will not hesitate. O son of Adam,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40466,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/06\/07\/rizq-salat-zakat\/","url_meta":{"origin":25262,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Wealth: Allah provides for charity, not indulgence","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 7, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Waqid reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah said: Verily, We have sent down wealth for the performance of prayer and offering charity. If the son of Adam owned a valley, he would like to have a second. If he had two valleys,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33792,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/11\/20\/hasan-never-forgot-his-sins\/","url_meta":{"origin":25262,"position":3},"title":"Hasan on Fear: He enters Paradise because he never forgot his sins","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 20, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Hisham ibn Hassan reported: Al-Hasan al-Basri, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cVerily, a man may commit a sin and he never forgets it, always fearing it, until he enters Paradise.\u201d Source: al-Zuhd li-Ah\u0323mad ibn H\u0323anbal 1581 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0647\u0650